e: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">2000.07</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">至2005.02&nbsp;&nbsp; 郑州轻工业学院计算机系任助教；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">2005.03</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">至2010.02&nbsp;&nbsp; 郑州轻工业学院计算机系任讲师；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">2010.03</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">至今&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 郑州轻工业学院软件学院任副教授。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black\">&nbsp;</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width: medium 2px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor rgb(0, 102, 153) rgb(0, 102, 153); padding: 0px 7px;\" colspan=\"6\" width=\"659\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">【主讲课程】:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;text-align: left;text-indent: 8px;margin-top: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">Oracle</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">数据库技术、数据库原理、数据库技术及应用、Java程序设计</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width: medium 2px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor rgb(0, 102, 153) rgb(0, 102, 153); padding: 0px 7px;\" colspan=\"6\" width=\"659\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">【研究领域】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">数据库技术</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width: medium 2px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor rgb(0, 102, 153) rgb(0, 102, 153); padding: 0px 7px;\" colspan=\"6\" width=\"659\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">【主要荣誉】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">校“三育人”先进个人、校师德先进个人、全国软件设计大赛优秀指导教师</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width: medium 2px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor rgb(0, 102, 153) rgb(0, 102, 153); padding: 0px 7px;\" colspan=\"6\" width=\"659\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">【社会兼职】</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">ORACLE Academy</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">会员</span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width: medium 2px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor rgb(0, 102, 153) rgb(0, 102, 153); padding: 0px 7px;\" colspan=\"6\" width=\"659\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">【科研成果】（论文、著作、项目、获奖、专利等）</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;text-align: left;text-indent: 32px;margin-top: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: #0a628b\">长期以来一直从事计算机、数据库等方面的教学与研究工作。近五年来，科研方面，在国内外重要的学术期刊和会议上发表论文11篇，其中EI、ISTP检索4篇；以主编、副主编参编著作7部。参与、主持了4项省厅级项目，通过省级鉴定项目4项，获省级教学成果奖励2项，在研项目1项。</span></p><p style=\";text-align: left;line-height: 125%;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 125%\">期刊论文： </span></strong></p><p style=\";text-align: left;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">[1] </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">梁树军</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">，程静</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">基于质心的改进型粒子群优化算法</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">，科学技术与工程，第11期，3109-3112页，2013； </span></p><p style=\";text-align: left;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">[2] </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">梁树军，</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">张志锋</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">.</span> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">基于构件技术和</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">B</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">方法的形式化需求分析</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">，郑州轻工业学院学报，第</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">24</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">卷，第</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">期，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">48-50</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">页，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">2009</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">；</span></p><p style=\";text-align: left;margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%;margin-top: auto;margin-bottom: auto\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">[3] </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">梁树军</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">，程静</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">.</span> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">基于</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: black;line-height: 150%\">LonMark</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">对象的智能节点研究，电脑与信息技术，第</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">17</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">卷，第</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">期，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">76-78</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">页，</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: black;line-height: 150%\">2009</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 楷体_GB2312;color: black;line-height: 150%\">；</span></p><p style=\";text-align: left;margin-left: 24px;line-heig